##############################################################################
#  URFD G3 Terminal Options
#
#  Configures Icom Terminal/Access Point mode (G3 protocol).
#  One option per line.
#
#  Options:
#    address <ip>       Public IP for terminal route responder.
#                        Leave unset if running on a public IP.
#                        Set to public IP if behind NAT/router.
#    modules <modules>  Modules that accept terminal connections.
#                        Default: * (all modules)
#
#  Examples:
#    address 203.0.113.1
#    modules BCD
#
##############################################################################
#address 203.0.113.1
#modules BCD
